								type[]=
								{
									"STRING"
								};
							};
							value="A Rebel offensive was launched last week and it collapsed our front, most units made it to the secondary line intact. Rumour has spread that a contingent of Takistani soldiers were captured while providing rear-guard, threats by the rebel leadership confirmed this rumour.<br/><br/>The lines have now stabilized and the Takistani Special Forces brigade and their Mechanised elements have arrived to lead the counter-attack, we recommend clearing the southern approach of the city to begin with then move towards the east.<br/><br/>You must crush the forces surrounding the town and then make a final assault to rescue the friendly contingent. We have confirmed 4 prisoners of war, proceed with extreme caution while breaching the construction site.<br/><br/>Let me clarify, you do not need to sweep the entire town, battalions are now forming up to complete the sweep and your priority is weakening their armored capacity and rescuing our soldiers.<br/><br/>Godspeed.";
